title: Chris Harris, Mike Musto
description: This week our guests are Chris Harris and Mike Musto, Matt and Chris join us from Wales where they've been busy filming, meanwhile we sit down with Musto and talk tiny electric cars, GM's Code 130R FRS/BRZ fighter, the Audi R8 V10+, and custom builds.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
